To implement real-time status updates for user requests, we can leverage Websockets with Flask-SocketIO. This will ensure that users receive notifications in real-time as the status of their requests changes.

Epic Title: Real-time Status Updates

We will create the necessary files, including models, services, controllers, and routes, to handle and broadcast real-time updates. Additionally, we'll ensure our frontend can receive and display these updates.

